      "rationale": "Relative hemolysis index RH computed for all 5 operating points. Mean absolute error 8.3% against experimental reference; within validation uncertainty of 12.1% (95% CI). Pressure rise prediction error < 4.5% across operating range. Formal validation metric E% reported per ASME V&V 20."
