    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 at MRL 2. Validation evidence demonstrates RH < 1 across all 5 operating points with validation uncertainty within acceptable bounds. The CFD model is accepted as sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
